messages.messageBody:
WARNING:
-=
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-3JCESdFNyw

I thought Duncan was going to bust a gut! <G>

Just thought we'd share!
===========================================================

Sandra's note:

This would be kind of scary for some kids, because there are some
images that are just fun, but many that are fairly gross.

I wouldn't have wanted to have seen that when I was little. It's
clever; parts are a lot like some of the Monty Python animation that
Terry Gilliam used to do. Some things can't be unseen, though, so
sensitive moms might not want to see it, and moms of sensitive kids
might want to preview it.





Please, anyone, before you post a link to an article or video or
pictures, tell us why, say something personal about what it is and
why you brought the link. When I'm not the listowner, I don't even
go to links posted without intro, but as listowner I felt a duty.

Sandra
